snippet.title: Tinkertown: 10 Minutes of Gameplay | Gamescom 2020
snippet.description: Check out exclusive gameplay of Tinkertown, a multiplayer sandbox game that looks a bit like what might happen if The Legend of Zelda: A Link to The Past were mixed with Terraria, debuted during gamescom 2020 presented by IGN.
